OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShetland will be rather cloudy
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain in the morning
OL,7,Fbefore becoming drier in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Orkney mostly dry and
OL,9,Fcloudy or bright.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy and murky evening
OL,12,Fwith some mist and patchy drizzle.
OL,13,FRemaining rather cloudy through the
OL,14,Frest of the night, but some clearer
OL,15,Fspells developing later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA mainly dry day with a
OL,18,Fgood deal of cloud, but some brighter
OL,19,For sunnier spells possible at times,
OL,20,Fespecially for Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
