OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FFairly cloudy with heavy and thundery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain on Thursday and
OL,8,FFriday alongside risk of haar. Fresher
OL,9,Fon Saturday with a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
